snippet.title: Lazr A Clothformer - District H1 Trailer
snippet.description:
The New Lazr Demo is live - get it at:
https://mrgrak.itch.io/lazr 
https://mrgrak.itch.io/lazrdemo

Lazr's kickstarter runs from January 25th to the end of Feb 2020.
Check out the kickstarter here: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lazr/lazr-a-cyberpunk-clothformer

Wishlist Lazr on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1181040/LAZR__A_Clothformer/

Visit the official Lazr website: https://lazr.online
You can follow daily development of Lazr on twitter:
@_mrgrak
